# | '_ ` _ \| |/ / _ \     Welcome to mko's i3 config!
# | | | | | |   < (_) |    nothing special here, pretty bare bones actually
# |_| |_| |_|_|\_\___/     if you need help, https://i3wm.org/docs/ check out the docs
